//Morphology myocardium

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Cardio MRI

When I select 'Focal myocardial edema' from 'Myocardial edema' dropdown menu
Then 'Edema' localizer is enabled

When I select 'Diffuse myocardial edema' from 'Myocardial edema' dropdown menu
Then 'Edema' localizer is disabled

When I select 'Focal wall thickening' from 'Wall thickening' dropdown menu
Then 'Thick' localizer is enabled

When I select 'Focal wall thinning' from 'Wall thinning ' dropdown menu
Then 'Thin' localizer is enabled

When I select 'Diffuse wall thinning' from 'Wall thinning ' dropdown menu
Then 'Thin' localizer is disabled

When I select 'Dissuse wall thinning' from 'Wall thinning ' dropdown menu
Then 'Thin' localizer is disabled

When I select 'Hypointensity in T1w/T2w focal' from 'Hypointensity' dropdown menu
Then 'Hypo' localizer is enabled

When I select 'Hypointensity in T1w/T2w diffuse' from 'Hypointensity' dropdown menu
Then 'Hypo' localizer is disabled
